text: The Farglory 95rich () is a skyscraper located in Xinzhuang District, New Taipei, Taiwan. It is the eleventh tallest building in Taiwan and the third tallest in New Taipei City(after Far Eastern Mega Tower, Neo Sky Dome). The height of building is 184.4 m, the floor area is 69,637.45m2, and it comprises 42 floors above ground, as well as 5 basement levels. == See also == * List of tallest buildings in Taiwan ==References== Category:2017 establishments in Taiwan Category:Office buildings completed in 2017 Category:Skyscrapers in New Taipei
title: Farglory 95rich
